page.title: 02HANNAH'S DAY IN HONLEY (1)
page.content: 08.09-I arose at this time and went to the toilet. 08.30-I had breakfast of "Sugar Puffs" 09.00-Watched television. 09.15-Dressed and read Friday's newspaper. 09.30-Watched more television. 09.38-Went to see who had knocked on the front door. 09.40-Went to wait for my dad. 09.45-Played tennis against the wall. 10.03-Watched a cartoon on television. 10.30-Went swimming at Holmfirth pool. 11.10-Shopping expedition planned and executed. 12.00-My football stickers were placed carefully in my album. 13.20-Paid a visit to toilet, washed my hands and had lunch. 14.09-After lunch I had the privilage of washing up!
